cdata.name: Auctus
cdata.desc:
Auctus isan Ethereum-basedretirement plan platform. It allows users to create diversified portfolios, consisting of traditional asset classes and cryptocurrencies. Auctus' mission is to empower the retirement saver and provide the information needed to take well-informed decisions by utilizing Ethereum smart contracts and robo advisory.

AUC is an ERC20 token that serves as a currency onAuctus' platform.
